- Always use tokenized Tailwind classes (bg-primary, text-foreground, border-border, bg-background, etc.).
- Prefer composing from UI primitives in src/components/ui/*.
- Never use raw hex colors in components (only CSS vars or Tailwind tokens).
- Use consistent layout rhythm: max-w-6xl/7xl, px-6, py-6, gap-6.
- Typography scale: page title text-2xl/3xl, section titles text-lg, body text-sm/base.
- Surfaces: Card for grouped content; rounded-xl; subtle borders; shadow-sm.
- Empty states must include: icon, headline, helper text, primary CTA.
- Buttons: default is primary orange; links should not be browser-default blue/underlined.
